												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "these characters are robbing an abandoned chapel and the roof in one of the rooms just collapsed. They don't know what's happening and are VERY twitchy. The roof in one of the rooms just collapsed, and they're reacting to the sound. This guy is the pragmatic one of the bandit group - robbing crypts is dangerous work, and he knows it. Doesn't necessarily like it though"
